	<p>We help clients select the proper entity for their businesses and provide advice about the tax and liability-limiting benefits and effects of the various forms of doing business. </p>
<p>Once formed, we can manage the maintenance of the entity, including periodic state reporting requirements. As changes occur in the laws governing entity structures, we alert our clients so that they may benefit from advantageous developments in the law. We provide day-to-day advice on all aspects of entity operations, from compliance to director duties.</p>
